<HEADLINE>
FRAZIER UPSETS TAUZIAT
</HEADLINE>
 (CORRECTS NEWSPAPER AFFILIATION) (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By JOE STEVENS  
 c.1999 Long Beach Press-Telegram  
