<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-10 13:39 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1837 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-LEVINGSTON-COLUMN-BOS     08-10 0637
