   LA SHOOTING:
</P>
<P>
   A gunman opened fire at a Jewish community center today injuring
at least two people. Police are still searching for the suspect.
</P>
<P>
   We have a staff photographer en route to the scene and expect to
move photos by 6:00 p.m. EDT. We are also monitoring our partners
to see if additional photos will be available.
</P>
<P>
   Please check GRAPHIC BUDGET moving at 6:30 p.m. EDT, for
graphics and maps to accompany this story.
</P>
<P>
   We will advise further on photos when more information is
available.
</P>
