   GOLF
</P>
<P>
   GLF-PGATIGER _ Everything Tiger Woods does lately turns out
golden. He won a made-for-prime time-TV match against David Duval
and pocketed $700,000. He's won three events this year and hasn't
missed a cut in his last 15 tournaments. All this points to Woods
