</P>
<P>
   &UR; (PLEASE NOTE: This article has been transmitted twice _ into the
``l'' lifestyle news and ``a'' general news files.) &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   ----- This article is also available in Spanish.-----
</P>
<P>
   &UR; By KEVIN KRAJICK &LR;  &QC; 
 &UR; c.1999 Discover magazine &LR;  &QC; 
 &UR; (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) &LR;  &QC;
</P>
