<P>
   UNDATED _ Corporal punishment in schools is legal in 23 states,
mostly in the South. The South remains not only the Bible Belt but
also the Spanking Belt, a place where ``spare the rod, spoil the
child'' is taken literally, and, sometimes, in the worst case, to
extremes. .MDBU/.MDRV/.MDUL/.MDBO/.MDNM/By JESSIE MILLIGAN. Story
will move in ``n'' regional category to Texas points. Accompanied
by BC-SCHOOL-PADDLING-LETTER, BC-SCHOOL PADDLING-STATES. &QL; 
