<P>
   UNDATED _ Memories should not be done in misty watercolors. I
like my memories vivid and distinct, with all the sights, smells
and sounds of the moment. By MONICA FRAZIER ANDERSON. Story will
move in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
